1891 ca : The family of Czar Aleksandr III ( 1845-1894 ). Right in the image of the Tsar, his wife left front Czarine Maria Fedorovna Dagmar of Denmark (1847-1928) , left the eldest son, Nikolai , later Czar Nicholas II . In this photo the others sons: George Alexandrovich (1871-1899), Xenia Alexandrovna (1875-1960, later married with Grand Duke Alexander Mikhailovich ), Michael Alexandrovich (1878-1918, later married with Natalia Brassova ) and Olga Alexandrovna (1882-1960 , later married with Duke Peter Alexandrovich of Oldenburg and after with Colonel Nikolai Alexandrovich Kulikovsky ).
